1. Install karma globally (if not previously installed)
    npm install karma-cli -g   (if not previously installed)

2. Install all necessary packages:
    npm install jasmine-core --save-dev
    npm install karma-jasmine --save-dev
    npm install phantomjs karma-phantomjs-launcher karma-chrome-launcher --save-dev

3. Install testem globaly (if not previously installed):
    npm install testem -g

4. Configure environment in testem.json

5. Run: testem
